with Mr. Song and Mr. Zheng.

158
00:18:44,447 --> 00:18:48,442
You must take her coat.

159
00:18:50,640 --> 00:18:52,738
Don't step on it!

160
00:18:52,838 --> 00:18:54,635
Mustn't get it dirty.

161
00:18:54,735 --> 00:18:57,233
Take her hat too.

162
00:18:57,333 --> 00:18:59,829
Right hand is for the coat.
Left hand is for the hat.

163
00:19:00,029 --> 00:19:01,428
That's the rule.

164
00:19:02,826 --> 00:19:05,323
Remember the way.

165
00:19:06,622 --> 00:19:09,518
