bring it at once. Got it?

184
00:20:30,822 --> 00:20:32,121
Got it.

185
00:20:32,221 --> 00:20:33,520
Put it on the sofa.

186
00:20:33,620 --> 00:20:36,616
Stand there and let me see.

187
00:20:47,503 --> 00:20:50,499
This way a little.

188
00:20:51,099 --> 00:20:53,396
Bow your head.

189
00:20:53,496 --> 00:20:55,094
Not bad.

190
00:20:55,293 --> 00:20:56,992
Don't forget...

191
00:20:57,092 --> 00:20:59,788
