at something...

192
00:20:59,888 --> 00:21:02,585
do it discreetly.

193
00:21:02,685 --> 00:21:04,383
Don't stare...

194
00:21:04,483 --> 00:21:08,778
or you'll end up
looking like an idiot.

195
00:21:09,676 --> 00:21:12,274
Don't complain.

196
00:21:12,374 --> 00:21:16,269
In a few years you'll be somebody
in Shanghai!

197
00:21:16,369 --> 00:21:20,264
Being a Tang
will change your life.

198
00:21:20,364 --> 00:21:21,663
Got it?

199
