Got it.

200
00:21:23,461 --> 00:21:25,058
The Boss is in there.

201
00:21:29,154 --> 00:21:30,552
Take a good look.

202
00:21:30,752 --> 00:21:33,649
If he's talking business
in that room...

203
00:21:33,749 --> 00:21:35,946
like now...

204
00:21:36,146 --> 00:21:37,744
