01:01:58,097 --> 01:02:00,794
Ajiao come here.

551
01:02:08,384 --> 01:02:13,280
Who is prettier?
Your mother or me?

552
01:02:16,975 --> 01:02:19,571
What doyou want to be
when you grow up?

553
01:02:21,170 --> 01:02:23,068
Come on tell me.

554
01:02:23,966 --> 01:02:25,665
I want to be like you.

555
01:02:25,764 --> 01:02:26,863
Ajiao!

556
01:02:32,657 --> 01:02:35,753
Have you been living here long?

557
01:02:35,853 --> 01:02:37,751
Several years.

558
01:02:38,150 --> 01:02:41,047
How can anybody live here?

559
01:02:41,546 --> 01:02:46,041
I'm bored to death
after just one day.

560
01:03:21,998 --> 01:03:25,794
Shuisheng! Do you know
where Miss is going?

561
01:03:26,593 --> 01:03:28,591
Go with her!

562
01:03:28,691 --> 01:03:33,685
Take an umbrella it's starting to rain.
Do you hear me?

563
01:03:33,884 --> 01:03:38,180
Shuisheng! Are you asleep?
Get up!

564
01:03:38,479 --> 01:03:41,276
Shuisheng! Get up! Quick!

565
01:04:25,823 --> 01:04:27,322
Buzz off!

566
01:04:27,921 --> 01:04:29,818
Go on go away!

567
01:04:53,391 --> 01:04:55,288
Open up!

568
01:04:56,387 --> 01:04:57,986
Who is it?

569
01:04:58,185 --> 01:05:01,082
It's me. I need you.

570
01:05:01,581 --> 01:05:04,677
Can't it wait till tomorrow?

571
01:05:05,277 --> 01:05:06,975
Open up!

572
01:05:08,573 --> 01:05:11,769
Are you counting your money
or what?

573
01:05:11,869 --> 01:05:14,367
I haven't come to borrow money!

574
01:05:16,064 --> 01:05:18,761
You took your time!

575
01:05:19,261 --> 01:05:21,857
-Were you asleep?
-Yes.

576
01:05:22,557 --> 01:05:24,853
On your own?

577
01:05:25,453 --> 01:05:27,551
Ajiao's sleeping too.

578
01:05:33,544 --> 01:05:36,540
I can't sleep on my own...

579
01:05:37,239 --> 01:05:40,235
so I came to talk to you.

580
01:05:41,534 --> 01:05:43,532
What about?

581
01:05:44,630 --> 01:05:47,228
Oh we'll think of something.

582
01:05:55,717 --> 01:05:58,115
If you don't want to never mind.

583
01:05:58,215 --> 01:06:01,011
I'll go. I'm going.

584
01:06:06,305 --> 01:06:08,802
Can I borrow some clothes?

585
01:06:08,902 --> 01:06:13,297
All mine are being washed.
I have nothing to wear.

586
01:06:13,797 --> 01:06:16,693
I have only peasant's clothes.

587
01:06:16,992 --> 01:06:18,891
They'll do fine.

588
01:06:19,889 --> 01:06:20,688
Miss!

589
01:06:25,882 --> 01:06:29,578
See how ignorant I am
about countryways?

590
01:06:29,678 --> 01:06:32,974
Walking into your bedroom
uninvited!

591
01:06:33,274 --> 01:06:35,271
Do sit down.

592
01:06:35,770 --> 01:06:37,668
No no.

593
01:06:39,167 --> 01:06:41,064
Thanks.

594
01:06:44,061 --> 01:06:46,857
Give me any old thing.

595
01:06:52,351 --> 01:06:54,848
Don't worry. Take your time.

596
01:06:55,247 --> 01:06:59,743
Besides I've got nothing else to do.

597
01:06:59,843 --> 01:07:02,739
I can't sleep on my own.

598
01:07:09,431 --> 01:07:12,128
Here! I've found something.

599
01:07:17,321 --> 01:07:20,118
You sew very well.

600
01:07:21,916 --> 01:07:25,611
If I were a man
I'd marry you myself.

601
01:07:25,711 --> 01:07:29,408
I wouldn't leave you
in somebody else's arms!

602
01:07:40,294 --> 01:07:43,291
I really have to go.

603
01:07:43,391 --> 01:07:47,986
Since you sleep alone
be sure to lock the door!

604
01:07:49,984 --> 01:07:52,980
I beg you go away

605
01:07:54,378 --> 01:07:57,874
Go quickly far away

606
01:07:57,974 --> 01:08:02,468
Go quickly far away

607
01:08:06,463 --> 01:08:12,357
SIXTH DAY

608
01:08:39,425 --> 01:08:42,122
Are those Mommy's clothes?

609
01:08:42,521 --> 01:08:44,120
Aren't they pretty?

610
01:08:44,419 --> 01:08:45,318
Yes!

611
01:08:46,217 --> 01:08:49,114
So pretty I'm going to keep them.

612
01:08:49,214 --> 01:08:51,510
I'm swapping clothes with her.

613
01:08:51,610 --> 01:08:54,707
Now you can call me " Mommy"...

614
01:08:54,807 --> 01:08:58,702
and you can call her " Miss."

615
01:09:00,601 --> 01:09:03,097
Teach me to sing.

616
01:09:03,197 --> 01:09:07,492
Shuisheng says
you sing very well.

617
01:09:09,989 --> 01:09:13,385
Ajiao can you sing?

618
01:09:13,485 --> 01:09:15,982
I only know one song.

619
01:09:16,381 --> 01:09:19,878
Then sing it for me.

620
01:09:19,978 --> 01:09:21,775
Go on sing!

621
01:09:21,875 --> 01:09:24,872
If you sing well
I'll give you lessons.

622
01:09:26,269 --> 01:09:30,765
Come on get up and sing!
Up you get!

623
01:09:34,261 --> 01:09:35,360
Sing!

624
01:09:40,952 --> 01:09:42,750
Sing!

625
01:09:44,049 --> 01:09:48,144
Beddy-bye beddy-bye
Over Grandma's bridge

626
01:09:48,244 --> 01:09:52,239
Grandma says I'm good as gold

627
01:09:52,439 --> 01:09:54,337
I know how to laugh

628
01:09:54,437 --> 01:09:56,334
I know how to cry

629
01:09:56,434 --> 01:10:00,530
Two yellow dogs carry the litter

630
01:10:04,425 --> 01:10:07,821
On the bridge
the birds are tweeting

631
01:10:08,220 --> 01:10:10,618
Do you know this song?

632
01:10:11,416 --> 01:10:14,913
My grandma sang it to me
when I was little.

633
01:10:16,012 --> 01:10:18,708
In her red trousers
and coat of brocade

634
01:10:18,808 --> 01:10:22,404
Grandma takes me to the litter

635
01:10:22,504 --> 01:10:26,399
Beddy-bye beddy-bye
Over Grandma's bridge

636
01:10:38,785 --> 01:10:41,581
Sing Shuisheng. All together!

637
01:11:31,223 --> 01:11:34,219
So what
if I had him killed?

638
01:11:35,019 --> 01:11:37,615
I gave the orders.

639
01:11:37,715 --> 01:11:40,812
Nobody lands or leaves
without permission.

640
01:11:40,912 --> 01:11:42,409
He didn't bother you!

641
01:11:42,509 --> 01:11:46,605
That's not my problem!
We have to be careful.

642
01:11:49,102 --> 01:11:51,898
Stop making such a fuss!

643
01:11:52,198 --> 01:11:56,992
If you minded your own business
he would still be alive.

644
01:11:57,392 --> 01:11:59,090
To tell you the truth...

645
01:11:59,789 --> 01:12:04,284
if you had kept quiet last night
I'd have been none the wiser.

646
01:12:05,982 --> 01:12:07,880
I owe you my thanks.

647
01:12:08,179 --> 01:12:11,875
Whom are you trying to blame?
Not me!

648
01:12:11,975 --> 01:12:13,673
It's all your fault!

649
01:12:53,926 --> 01:12:55,524
Stop.

650
01:12:58,120 --> 01:13:02,116
Did you hear me
and the Boss arguing?

651
01:13:03,015 --> 01:13:06,511
The Tang family is all bad.

652
01:13:14,701 --> 01:13:17,298
Can't you sleep?

653
01:13:20,395 --> 01:13:22,591
Then stay and talk to me.

654
01:13:28,385 --> 01:13:31,881
Do you know how to climb trees?

655
01:13:32,181 --> 01:13:33,479
Yes.

656
01:13:35,077 --> 01:13:37,175
When I was a girl...

657
01:13:37,274 --> 01:13:39,972
we had two trees in the yard.

658
01:13:40,071 --> 01:13:41,670
Mulberry trees.

659
01:13:41,770 --> 01:13:44,466
Very very tall ones.

660
01:13:44,566 --> 01:13:48,261
People say mulberry trees
in the yard...

661
01:13:48,361 --> 01:13:50,459
bring good luck.

662
01:13:50,959 --> 01:13:56,053
Every summer
they bore lots offruit.

663
01:13:56,153 --> 01:13:58,649
People came to pick them.

664
01:13:59,049 --> 01:14:00,547
And I...

665
01:14:01,746 --> 01:14:06,441
I climbed up in the tree
and ate lots of them.

666
01:14:10,735 --> 01:14:14,731
See I'm a country bumpkin too.

667
01:14:15,530 --> 01:14:18,226
Bijou the bumpkin.

668
01:14:18,826 --> 01:14:21,323
Bijou the bumpkin!

669
01:14:35,007 --> 01:14:39,601
Other than your uncle
have you got any family in Shanghai?

670
01:14:56,082 --> 01:14:57,481
Take this.

671
01:14:58,379 --> 01:15:00,377
Take it!

672
01:15:11,464 --> 01:15:14,960
When you've saved up enough
to open a shop...

673
01:15:15,060 --> 01:15:17,457
go back to the country.

674
01:15:17,856 --> 01:15:19,754
Shanghai is all bad.

675
01:15:20,353 --> 01:15:22,551
I want to avenge my uncle.

676
01:15:22,651 --> 01:15:25,947
The Boss said his eyes cried out
for vengeance.

677
01:15:26,446 --> 01:15:30,342
Oh yeah?
So go back to Shanghai.

678
01:15:31,141 --> 01:15:34,736
Be like your uncle.
Go back to Shanghai and get killed.

679
01:15:34,836 --> 01:15:37,234
Go on go to bed.

680
01:16:20,483 --> 01:16:24,877
Cuihua this evening
you and I can have a chat.

681
01:16:32,769 --> 01:16:35,465
-Hello Miss!
-Hard at work?

682
01:16:36,364 --> 01:16:39,260
Take a seat Miss.

683
01:16:49,249 --> 01:16:51,247
How old are you?

684
01:16:51,446 --> 01:16:52,545
I'm a Horse.

685
01:16:52,645 --> 01:16:54,343
A Horse?

686
01:16:54,642 --> 01:16:56,940
You look much older!

687
01:16:57,040 --> 01:16:59,936
Yet you're younger than me.

688
01:17:00,735 --> 01:17:04,730
When you look old
the mosquitos don't bite.

689
01:17:07,028 --> 01:17:09,325
Why don't you remarry?

690
01:17:11,822 --> 01:17:14,419
Surely there's somebody.

691
01:17:15,118 --> 01:17:19,513
There must be a man
in your life.

692
01:17:20,512 --> 01:17:22,410
I could find you one.

693
01:17:22,510 --> 01:17:25,406
Uncle likes Mommy a lot.

694
01:17:25,506 --> 01:17:28,403
Ajiao! Go to bed.

695
01:17:35,894 --> 01:17:37,792
Who is Uncle?

696
01:17:38,491 --> 01:17:41,787
He lives on the island
across the way.

697
01:17:42,087 --> 01:17:43,585
Does he visit often?

698
01:17:43,684 --> 01:17:45,782
He comes by boat in the night.

699
01:17:45,882 --> 01:17:48,380
Ajiao! Go to bed!

700
01:17:54,971 --> 01:17:57,968
When are you getting married?

701
01:17:58,966 --> 01:18:01,264
After the New Year.

702
01:18:04,860 --> 01:18:09,154
Forget that man.

703
01:18:09,954 --> 01:18:12,551
Why live in the country?

704
01:18:13,450 --> 01:18:17,246
Come to Shanghai with me.

705
01:18:17,345 --> 01:18:21,740
I'll find you a good husband.

706
01:18:22,240 --> 01:18:25,735
You can keep Ajiao with you.

707
01:18:25,835 --> 01:18:28,632
If you don't want to
I'll keep her.

708
01:18:28,932 --> 01:18:31,129
I like that girl.

709
01:18:31,229 --> 01:18:33,926
What are you saying Miss?

710
01:18:34,425 --> 01:18:36,523
I mean it.

711
01:18:36,623 --> 01:18:39,619
I came here to talk about it.

712
01:18:41,517 --> 01:18:45,012
But I don't want to leave here.

713
01:18:49,607 --> 01:18:52,304
You really want to stay?

714
01:18:55,400 --> 01:18:57,498
Well in that case...

715
01:18:57,698 --> 01:19:01,094
let me know
when you get married.

716
01:19:01,493 --> 01:19:04,389
I'll give you
a wedding trousseau.

717
01:19:04,489 --> 01:19:09,483
I'll send clothes
for you and Ajiao...

718
01:19:09,883 --> 01:19:14,478
and I'll send
an opera company...

719
01:19:14,577 --> 01:19:16,576
to sing for you.

720
01:19:17,175 --> 01:19:19,771
You're making fun of me.

721
01:19:20,171 --> 01:19:22,569
Everything's planned.

722
01:19:22,669 --> 01:19:26,564
For the wedding
he'll simply move in here.

723
01:19:32,357 --> 01:19:36,352
You must have had
a grand wedding!

724
01:19:36,452 --> 01:19:39,448
Married me?

725
01:19:41,147 --> 01:19:43,844
It's too soon for that!

726
01:19:45,541 --> 01:19:48,838
At your age
you ought to be married.

727
01:19:48,938 --> 01:19:53,832
Oh sure. I ought to.

728
01:19:54,132 --> 01:19:57,228
But I can't see who to.

729
01:19:57,328 --> 01:20:00,623
I don't know anyone worth it.

730
01:20:01,023 --> 01:20:05,618
You have to be patient
with a man.

731
01:20:06,717 --> 01:20:10,612
Be sincere
and he will treat you right.

732
01:20:12,610 --> 01:20:17,504
I've been sincere so many times.

733
01:20:19,202 --> 01:20:21,899
You'll find your Mr. Right.

734
01:20:22,698 --> 01:20:27,692
Up to now I've been unlucky.

735
01:20:27,992 --> 01:20:33,585
Now I'm with her uncle
and I'm happy.

736
01:20:41,875 --> 01:20:43,773
Cuihua...

737
01:20:45,870 --> 01:20:48,268
I'm sorry.

738
01:20:49,567 --> 01:20:52,163
I shouldn't have come.

739
01:20:52,663 --> 01:20:55,958
What makes you say that?

740
01:20:57,357 --> 01:20:58,955
Really...

741
01:21:00,153 --> 01:21:02,751
I shouldn't have come.

742
01:21:05,247 --> 01:21:08,544
I shouldn't have come
to this island.

743
01:21:08,644 --> 01:21:10,941
I'm truly sorry.

744
01:22:00,782 --> 01:22:02,580
Shuisheng!

745
01:22:12,169 --> 01:22:13,667
Were you waiting for me?

746
01:22:14,367 --> 01:22:16,664
I brought you the umbrella.

747
01:22:36,340 --> 01:22:40,635
Shuisheng
you must not stay with me.

748
01:22:41,035 --> 01:22:43,932
I'm not good to you.

749
01:23:02,909 --> 01:23:08,703
SEVENTH DAY

750
01:23:21,687 --> 01:23:24,085
Are you Cuihua?

751
01:23:24,984 --> 01:23:26,781
How do you know my name?

752
01:23:26,981 --> 01:23:31,376
I've eaten your fish soup
so I know your name.

753
01:23:33,274 --> 01:23:37,269
Are you Ajiao? Come here.

754
01:23:43,362 --> 01:23:44,461
Say "Grandpa."

755
01:23:44,561 --> 01:23:46,258
Grandpa.

756
01:23:47,257 --> 01:23:49,954
You're pretty.

757
01:23:50,554 --> 01:23:54,449
You look like Bijou
as a little girl.

758
01:23:56,246 --> 01:23:58,744
Bijou!

759
01:23:59,143 --> 01:24:01,440
Go get Miss.

760
01:24:08,732 --> 01:24:09,931
Bijou!

761
01:24:10,630 --> 01:24:13,826
Look at Ajiao.
She looks like you as a girl.

762
01:24:17,222 --> 01:24:22,116
Cuihua cook some fish.
We have guests tonight.

763
01:24:23,015 --> 01:24:24,214
Song and Zheng.

764
01:24:34,901 --> 01:24:38,797
Got the shits again you little prick?
Serves you right...

765
01:24:38,897 --> 01:24:41,593
for staying outdoors all night!

766
01:24:41,693 --> 01:24:44,990
It's your fault
you've got the shits!

767
01:24:45,189 --> 01:24:46,687
Move away!

768
01:24:46,887 --> 01:24:48,485
Move away!

769
01:27:00,530 --> 01:27:03,926
Shit it's going to rain!

770
01:27:04,026 --> 01:27:08,320
Good. It will make the job easier.

771
01:27:09,419 --> 01:27:12,815
Doesn't Song mind
about killing Bijou?

772
01:27:12,915 --> 01:27:16,811
Do as you're told.
Don't complicate things.

773
01:27:16,911 --> 01:27:19,907
Remember.
Once the bitch is asleep...

774
01:27:20,007 --> 01:27:24,701
strangle her.
Be careful not to make any noise.

775
01:27:24,801 --> 01:27:27,897
- Song said to stab her.
- What's it to you?

776
01:27:28,097 --> 01:27:32,492
Just don't disfigure her.

777
01:27:34,390 --> 01:27:37,286
It's raining.
Where do we hide?

778
01:27:37,586 --> 01:27:38,685
In the water.

779
01:27:39,184 --> 01:27:42,980
It'll be easy.
There aren't many of them.

780
01:28:27,427 --> 01:28:28,726
What's up Shuisheng?

781
01:28:30,624 --> 01:28:32,621
Don't you know the rule?

782
01:28:33,221 --> 01:28:35,518
Can't you see the Boss is here?

783
01:28:35,618 --> 01:28:37,915
If it's not urgent get out.

784
01:28:38,015 --> 01:28:41,711
Shuisheng? What's the matter?

785
01:28:42,111 --> 01:28:44,308
Miss! They want to kill you!

786
01:29:04,784 --> 01:29:08,979
Shuisheng calm down.
Take it easy.

787
01:29:09,078 --> 01:29:14,073
What did you hear?
What did you see?

788
01:29:14,372 --> 01:29:18,767
I heard two men.
They were planning to kill Miss.

789
01:29:18,867 --> 01:29:24,460
Shuisheng look at me.
Look at me! Explain yourself.

790
01:29:26,658 --> 01:29:30,154
I had the shits.
I was crouching down.

791
01:29:30,354 --> 01:29:32,452
- I heard two men.
- Saying what?

792
01:29:32,552 --> 01:29:36,846
They were going to kill Miss
with a knife.

793
01:29:37,246 --> 01:29:42,540
Shuisheng
who was going to kill Miss?

794
01:30:27,187 --> 01:30:31,082
How many men
did you come with Song?

795
01:30:36,776 --> 01:30:37,775
Two.

796
01:30:38,074 --> 01:30:42,669
That's a lie.
Two boats and 18 men right?

797
01:30:44,966 --> 01:30:46,764
Do you think Zheng is stupid?

798
01:30:49,660 --> 01:30:52,557
Why did you bring so many men?

799
01:30:52,657 --> 01:30:54,554
Just to kill Bijou?

800
01:30:54,954 --> 01:30:57,352
What did she do to you?

801
01:31:00,348 --> 01:31:03,344
Why meddle in my private life?

802
01:31:07,739 --> 01:31:09,936
Don't you get it yet?

803
01:31:10,136 --> 01:31:12,034
Then I'll explain.

804
01:31:13,532 --> 01:31:16,829
See Song there looking so serious?

805
01:31:16,929 --> 01:31:19,625
He actually works for Fat Yu.

806
01:31:19,725 --> 01:31:22,023
He came here...

807
01:31:22,222 --> 01:31:24,219
to kill us all.

808
01:31:29,114 --> 01:31:34,008
Do you think I've been twirling
my thumbs since we got here?

809
01:31:40,001 --> 01:31:41,999
On August 6th...

810
01:31:42,099 --> 01:31:45,395
after the police seized
those 80 packs of opium...

811
01:31:45,594 --> 01:31:49,989
the Boss invited
the customs officers to dinner.

812
01:31:50,089 --> 01:31:52,587
That night
our man watching Song...

813
01:31:52,687 --> 01:31:57,681
saw him go to Miss's house
for the first time.

814
01:31:57,880 --> 01:32:01,876
After that he went there often.
We have all the details.

815
01:32:02,575 --> 01:32:06,670
On the 3rd of this month
Fat Yu invited Song to dinner.

816
01:32:06,870 --> 01:32:09,466
They met secretly at a restaurant.

817
01:32:09,566 --> 01:32:12,963
The next evening the 4th...

818
01:32:13,063 --> 01:32:14,860
the Boss was attacked.

819
01:32:15,259 --> 01:32:21,253
Liu Agen Acha Aniu and Miaofa
were killed.

820
01:32:21,552 --> 01:32:24,349
The next day
the Boss came here to hide...

821
01:32:24,449 --> 01:32:27,346
protected by 40 of Zheng's men.

822
01:32:27,745 --> 01:32:32,340
Last night the Boss sent Zheng
to Shanghai...

823
01:32:32,440 --> 01:32:35,835
to invite Song to come here alone.

824
01:32:35,935 --> 01:32:42,528
But 18 of Song's men
arrived after dark.

825
01:32:51,417 --> 01:32:53,115
Song...

826
01:32:54,313 --> 01:32:59,208
I knew that you and Fat Yu
were out to get me in Shanghai.

827
01:33:01,206 --> 01:33:02,305
I also knew that...

828
01:33:02,404 --> 01:33:08,298
when you got Zheng's message
you'd send men here to kill me.

829
01:33:08,697 --> 01:33:13,591
What Shuisheng overheard
we already knew.

830
01:33:14,290 --> 01:33:16,787
I came to this godforsaken place...

831
01:33:16,887 --> 01:33:21,182
but the whole thing was planned...

832
01:33:21,282 --> 01:33:25,876
to set you up this evening.

833
01:33:29,971 --> 01:33:31,670
Now do you see?

834
01:33:37,463 --> 01:33:39,062
Song...

835
01:33:39,360 --> 01:33:42,857
do you want to see my wounds?

836
01:33:52,945 --> 01:33:56,640
Not one hole except my navel!

837
01:34:18,315 --> 01:34:19,913
Boss...

838
01:34:20,212 --> 01:34:24,208
you don't like
my " Moonlight" song.

839
01:34:27,604 --> 01:34:31,999
But Song often promised me...

840
01:34:32,498 --> 01:34:38,192
that once he had taken your place...

841
01:34:38,292 --> 01:34:41,488
I could sing it for him every day.

842
01:34:43,286 --> 01:34:47,980
He also said he would give me
the nightclub...

843
01:34:48,080 --> 01:34:52,575
so I could listen
to other people sing.

844
01:34:53,574 --> 01:34:56,670
He promised
we'd get married in France...

845
01:34:56,770 --> 01:35:02,163
and I would sing " Moonlight"
for him on our wedding day.

846
01:35:02,963 --> 01:35:05,159
Isn't that so Song?

847
01:35:12,651 --> 01:35:16,946
Far away the clouds are fading

848
01:35:17,046 --> 01:35:21,441
My lover appears in the moonlight

849
01:35:23,538 --> 01:35:27,434
I'll murder you! Bitch!
I'll kill you!

850
01:35:27,534 --> 01:35:29,532
Did you think I loved you?

851
01:35:29,731 --> 01:35:32,428
I loathe you!

852
01:35:32,727 --> 01:35:38,521
Seeing you with that old wreck
made me sick!

853
01:35:39,620 --> 01:35:43,715
You peasant bitch!
Who do you think you are?

854
01:35:43,815 --> 01:35:46,611
I never loved you!

855
01:35:46,811 --> 01:35:49,208
For the last five years...

856
01:35:49,308 --> 01:35:52,504
there wasn't a day
I didn't want to murder you.

857
01:35:53,803 --> 01:35:57,298
Listen Zheng and you too...

858
01:35:57,498 --> 01:35:59,596
listen to me!

859
01:35:59,796 --> 01:36:01,893
I wanted to kill him
not for my sake...

860
01:36:02,792 --> 01:36:05,688
but for the sake
of the Tang family!

861
01:36:06,288 --> 01:36:10,083
With me in charge
think what we'd have done!

862
01:36:13,480 --> 01:36:19,573
With me in charge
it would all be different!

863
01:36:19,773 --> 01:36:22,569
He's old. He's out of date!

864
01:36:50,535 --> 01:36:53,732
Shuisheng. There's no need
for you to stay.

865
01:36:53,832 --> 01:36:57,428
Go to bed. Go on.

866
01:37:01,323 --> 01:37:03,321
Run along.

867
01:37:11,911 --> 01:37:15,307
You can insult me all you like...

868
01:37:15,407 --> 01:37:20,600
but tonight we're going
to settle up the score.

869
01:38:09,044 --> 01:38:10,941
Not bad!

870
01:38:11,340 --> 01:38:13,339
You really are a hotshot.

871
01:38:13,438 --> 01:38:16,534
I didn't expect you to get up.

872
01:38:17,234 --> 01:38:21,628
Your 18 men are lying there.

873
01:38:22,228 --> 01:38:27,022
You'll have company Song!

874
01:38:27,322 --> 01:38:32,216
When I get back to Shanghai
I'll say that Fat Yu killed you.

875
01:38:32,815 --> 01:38:34,814
I'll wear mourning for you...

876
01:38:34,913 --> 01:38:39,308
to show all of Shanghai
how much I value my men.

877
01:38:39,908 --> 01:38:44,102
Zheng and I will kill Fat Yu
to avenge you.

878
01:38:44,302 --> 01:38:47,099
Shanghai is going to see some action!

879
01:38:47,198 --> 01:38:49,796
Too bad you won't be around to watch.

880
01:38:50,495 --> 01:38:54,790
Have you got a final wish?

881
01:38:55,090 --> 01:38:57,386
I'll grant it for you.

882
01:38:58,385 --> 01:39:00,384
I've said all I had to say.

883
01:39:00,583 --> 01:39:02,480
I wasn't going to speak again...

884
01:39:03,080 --> 01:39:05,777
but as you're in such a good mood...

885
01:39:05,877 --> 01:39:09,173
I'll say one more thing
to please you.

886
01:39:09,573 --> 01:39:11,769
You forgot one thing.

887
01:39:12,269 --> 01:39:16,065
Maybe you had me followed...

888
01:39:16,564 --> 01:39:20,560
but I could easily
have done the same to you.

889
01:39:42,833 --> 01:39:44,731
What do we do with him?

890
01:39:44,831 --> 01:39:47,028
Bury him alive.

891
01:40:29,478 --> 01:40:32,375
Since you had
a little act with Song...

892
01:40:32,475 --> 01:40:35,372
you're going to bow out with him.

893
01:40:35,472 --> 01:40:38,767
As they say you had it coming!

894
01:40:40,266 --> 01:40:44,561
I'm not going to publicize
your dirty little tricks.

895
01:40:45,260 --> 01:40:47,657
I'm not going to lose face.

896
01:40:47,757 --> 01:40:50,154
Nobodywill ever know.

897
01:40:50,254 --> 01:40:53,850
You will die as white as a lily.

898
01:40:55,148 --> 01:41:00,242
According to the rules
I will ask you one last question:

899
01:41:00,342 --> 01:41:02,040
Have you anything to say?

900
01:41:02,639 --> 01:41:05,436
Have you got a final wish?

901
01:41:07,333 --> 01:41:11,429
You know I never asked you
for anything before.

902
01:41:11,629 --> 01:41:13,626
Now I ask for just one thing.

903
01:41:14,026 --> 01:41:15,524
All right. Say it.

904
01:41:16,623 --> 01:41:20,519
Cuihua and Ajiao were not involved
in any of this.

905
01:41:20,818 --> 01:41:21,916
Don't touch them.

906
01:41:22,416 --> 01:41:25,013
Obviously I'm taking Ajiao with me.

907
01:41:25,113 --> 01:41:27,210
We'll take care of her.

908
01:41:27,310 --> 01:41:31,306
In a few years
she'll be a new Bijou.

909
01:41:33,003 --> 01:41:35,601
But as for Cuihua...

910
01:41:36,000 --> 01:41:37,498
it's too late.

911
01:41:38,997 --> 01:41:41,294
I didn't want to kill her...

912
01:41:41,394 --> 01:41:46,089
but since you talked to her
she knew too much.

913
01:41:46,288 --> 01:41:48,585
See? Your fault again.

914
01:41:52,181 --> 01:41:55,178
But that night...

915
01:41:55,378 --> 01:41:57,974
I told her nothing.

916
01:41:58,873 --> 01:42:01,171
I talked about myself...

917
01:42:01,271 --> 01:42:04,367
about my background.

918
01:42:09,061 --> 01:42:11,259
Cuihua...

919
01:42:12,257 --> 01:42:14,355
forgive me.

920
01:42:14,655 --> 01:42:16,952
Please forgive me.

921
01:42:17,950 --> 01:42:20,348
- I shouldn't have come.
- What was that?

922
01:42:26,341 --> 01:42:28,238
I said...

923
01:42:29,138 --> 01:42:31,335
you're a pig!

924
01:42:32,135 --> 01:42:34,132
An old pig! I'll kill you!

925
01:42:39,226 --> 01:42:41,024
I'll kill you!

926
01:42:48,315 --> 01:42:50,313
Miss!

927
01:43:52,440 --> 01:43:54,237
Come the spring...

928
01:43:54,437 --> 01:43:58,732
the grass on that island
will be good.

929
01:43:59,931 --> 01:44:02,328
You're right Boss.

930
01:44:05,424 --> 01:44:10,019
Grandpa you have to let
Shuisheng down!

931
01:44:10,119 --> 01:44:15,013
Later. It's not hurting him.
Don't worry.

932
01:44:15,712 --> 01:44:19,707
Ajiao did you never have a dog?

933
01:44:19,807 --> 01:44:20,806
No.

934
01:44:20,906 --> 01:44:23,703
A good dog has to be trained.

935
01:44:23,802 --> 01:44:26,800
That's what I'm doing to him.

936
01:44:28,797 --> 01:44:31,394
Where's Mommy? And Miss?

937
01:44:31,594 --> 01:44:33,591
Didn't you say...

938
01:44:33,691 --> 01:44:37,887
we would meet them
on the boat?

939
01:44:38,185 --> 01:44:43,080
They went away on another boat.

940
01:44:43,180 --> 01:44:46,876
We'll meet up with them
in Shanghai.

941
01:44:46,976 --> 01:44:49,073
Am I going to Shanghai?

942
01:44:49,173 --> 01:44:52,769
Yes we're on our way to Shanghai.

943
01:44:52,869 --> 01:44:55,765
In Shanghai
will I have pretty dresses?

944
01:44:55,865 --> 01:44:56,864
Yes.

945
01:44:56,964 --> 01:44:58,961
And lots of nice things?

946
01:44:59,061 --> 01:45:00,260
Sure!

947
01:45:00,360 --> 01:45:03,057
Lots of bracelets and rings.

948
01:45:04,555 --> 01:45:08,051
I want to be like Miss.

949
01:45:08,350 --> 01:45:12,046
All right. You'll be like Miss.

950
01:45:12,546 --> 01:45:15,142
You'll be like Miss.

951
01:45:27,428 --> 01:45:31,124
Beddy-bye beddy-bye
Over Grandma's bridge

952
01:45:31,523 --> 01:45:36,617
Grandma says I'm good as gold
I know how to laugh

953
01:45:36,917 --> 01:45:39,513
I know how to cry

954
01:45:39,613 --> 01:45:43,608
Two yellow dogs carry the litter